text: CIHW-FM is a Canadian radio station, which broadcasts to the Huron-Wendat Nation. Broadcasting on 100.3 FM, CIHW is a community radio station operated by the Huron-Wendat Nation at Wendake, an enclave of First Nations land within Quebec City. ==External links== * CIHW * CIHW-FM history - Canadian Communication Foundation * Ihw Ihw Category:Year of establishment missing
